_sText: Two Bases are seperated by breakable walls, break them to access the opponents side.  Don't fall into the pit of fiery death!!!  Loved this map back in the dayz, so much so, I had to remake it because it is nowhere to be found on the net or my old HD.  This is my first map ever, however I hope it doesn't show :P  Thanks to kaddar for creating the original over 6 years ago.  And a special thanks to [FF]Elite.Jack Daniels for being my mentor, brainstormer, and advisor throughout the whole creation process.  I would very much enjoy receiving feedback on this map.  I would like to tell you that it is tested and this is the final release, however it has not been tested on a large scale and it is not the final release.  The map is optimized and ready to be played on.  Up to 32 players can enjoy this map.  CCB = Cr4zYcH1cK3nB0Y.  If you need to tell me anything about this map, you can contact me through steam.  My steam is Cr4zYcH1cK3nB0Y.  Enjoy :)
